      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I've kept it in absolutely pristine condition and it's been loved so much! If you're looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the brand new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. It's super clean, runs like a dream, and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look and see for yourself, you're going to love it! \u2728",
