    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in museum-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS variable valve timing system that remains in peak factory specification. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis is impeccable, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing Bilstein dampers and OEM bushings to maintain original turn-in geometry. Every mechanical system, from the 11.5:1 compression ratio cylinders to the cross-drilled rotors, reflects a rigorous maintenance protocol. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist demanding mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
