    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true 'time capsule' specimen, presented in flawless showroom condition. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. It has been strictly garage-kept and recently treated to a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the upholstery shows zero wear, the dashboard is pristine, and it still retains that signature new-car aroma. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a complete, documented service history from certified specialists. It sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires and offers a drive that is as tight and responsive as the day it was delivered. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
